'''2011年O104:H4型大腸桿菌疫情'''於2011年5月[[德国|德国]]開始爆發，並造成多人死亡。新菌株'''[[大腸桿菌O104:H4型|O104:H4型大腸桿菌]]'''是導致[[食物中毒|食物中毒]]的主因。最早是出現數人在德國遭到細菌感染，進而併發[[溶血性尿毒综合征|溶血性尿毒综合征]]，陸續接受急診治療後，這波疫情就開始了。截至6月8日，由於疫情加劇，溶血性尿毒綜合症導致26人死亡，約500人入院。6月5日，德國[[下萨克森州|下萨克森州]]農業廳表示，[[比嫩比特尔|比嫩比特尔]]一家農場所生產的某一品種[[豆芽|豆芽]]，疑似為疫情爆發的源頭<ref name="CNN0605">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/06/05/europe.e.coli/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 |title=German-grown food named likely culprit in deadly outbreak |publisher=CNN.com |date=2010-06-05 |accessdate=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110042734/http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/06/05/europe.e.coli/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該農場目前已經關閉<ref name="CNN0605"/>。雖然下薩克森的實驗室在該農場產品中沒有檢測出任何致病的大腸桿菌，但不久後，[[北莱茵-威斯特法伦州|北莱茵-威斯特法伦州]]的一個實驗室在該農場一包已丟棄的豆芽菜中驗出致病菌株<ref name=thelocal110611>{{cite news|url=http://www.thelocal.de/national/20110610-35583.html|title=Deadly E. coli found on bean sprouts|publisher=www.thelocal.de|date=2010-06-11|accessdate=2011-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613003019/http://www.thelocal.de/national/20110610-35583.html|archive-date=2011-06-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

另外在德國境內，已通報4125宗病例，48人死亡（截至7月1日）<ref name="ECDC 1 July 2011" />。除了德國，也有零星病例發生在[[瑞士|瑞士]]<ref name="webseriestoday1">{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.webseriestoday.com/2011/06/health-alert-2011-e-coli-o104h4.html |title=Health Alert: 2011 E. coli O104:H4 outbreak |publisher=Web Series Today |date=2011-06-02 |accessdate=2011-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319213520/http://www.webseriestoday.com/2011/06/health-alert-2011-e-coli-o104h4.html |archive-date=2012-03-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 、[[波兰|波蘭]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>、[[荷兰|荷兰]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>、[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>、[[丹麦|丹麦]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>、[[英国|英国]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>、[[加拿大|加拿大]]<ref name="webseriestoday1"/>及[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/43227702/ns/health-infectious_diseases/ | title=E. Two in U.S. infected in German ''E. coli'' outbreak | publisher=MSNBC Online | date=2011-05-31 | accessdate=2011-06-02 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603020450/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/43227702/ns/health-infectious_diseases | archivedate=2011-06-03 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。基本上，所有被感染的患者在患病前不久都去過德國。

最初德國官員誤判致病[[大腸桿菌|大腸桿菌]]菌株的來源，並發佈這則錯誤消息<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/46118688-8c76-11e0-883f-00144feab49a.html?ftcamp=rss#axzz1OIkFWAJy |title=/ Europe - Cucumber crisis widens European rift |publisher=Ft.com |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603221348/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/46118688-8c76-11e0-883f-00144feab49a.html?ftcamp=rss#axzz1OIkFWAJy |archive-date=2011-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ec.europa.eu/food/food/docs/stec_outbreak_flash_report_27052011_en.pdf |title=EUROPEAN COMMISSION-Audio conference of the STEC OUTBREAK IN GERMANY |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103205239/http://ec.europa.eu/food/food/docs/stec_outbreak_flash_report_27052011_en.pdf |archivedate=2012-11-03 }}</ref><ref name=NOTIF_REFERENCE_20110703>{{Cite web |url=https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/rasff-window/portal/index.cfm?event=notificationDetail&NOTIF_REFERENCE=2011.0703 |title=RASFF Notification detail - 2011.0703 enterohaemorrhagic Escherichia coli in organic cucumbers from Spain |access-date=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807081209/https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/rasff-window/portal/index.cfm?event=notificationDetail&NOTIF_REFERENCE=2011.0703 |archive-date=2019-08-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=periscope>{{cite web |url=http://www.periscopepost.com/2011/06/e-coli-outbreak-sickens-european-diplomatic-relations/ |title=''E. coli'' outbreak sickens European diplomatic relations |publisher=The Periscope Post |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715064517/http://www.periscopepost.com/2011/06/e-coli-outbreak-sickens-european-diplomatic-relations/ |archive-date=2011-07-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德國衛生當局在還未得到檢測結果，便將O104血清型與[[西班牙|西班牙]]進口的[[黄瓜|小黄瓜]]連結在一起<ref name="globemail">{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/europe/toll-climbs-in-european-e-coli-outbreak/article2040566/ |title=Toll climbs in European ''E. coli'' outbreak |publisher=The Globe and Mail |date=2011-05-30 |accessdate=2011-05-31 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5z51R2yJm?url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/europe/toll-climbs-in-european-e-coli-outbreak/article2040566/ |archivedate=2011-05-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。不久他們才發現西班牙的溫室並非來源，這些小黃瓜樣本並沒有測出致病的大腸桿菌，和這波疫情無關<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ec.europa.eu/food/food/docs/stec_summary_note_audioconference_02062011_en.pdf |title=EUROPEAN COMMISSION - HEALTH AND CONSUMERS DIRECTORATE GENERAL - 2 June 2011 |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103214527/http://ec.europa.eu/food/food/docs/stec_summary_note_audioconference_02062011_en.pdf |archivedate=2012-11-03 }}</ref><ref name="eitb">{{cite web|url=http://www.eitb.com/news/life/detail/671223/germany-now-say-spanish-cucumbers-not-source-ecoli/|title=Germany now say Spanish cucumbers not source of ''E. coli''|publisher=Euskal Irrati Telebista|date=2011-05-31|accessdate=2011-05-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5z867uEEj?url=http://www.eitb.com/news/life/detail/671223/germany-now-say-spanish-cucumbers-not-source-ecoli/|archivedate=2011-06-02}}</ref>。西班牙隨後對德國的誤判表達強烈的憤怒，導致該國出口業每週2億[[美元|美元]]的損失<ref name="bbc3">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13605910|title=''E. coli'' cucumber scare: Spain angry at German claims|publisher=BBC|date=2011-05-31|accessdate=2011-05-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5z86Mgmsh?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13605910|archive-date=2011-06-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

疫情爆發後，[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]已禁止從[[欧盟|欧盟]]進口所有新鮮蔬菜。

