2011年5月2日，德國衛生當局報告該國正引爆一波稱為「[[溶血性尿毒綜合症|溶血性尿毒綜合症]]」的重症疫情<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices/outbreak-notice/2011-germany-europe-e-coli.htm |title=CDC - germany outbreak |publisher=C.cdc.gov |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110627161957/http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices/outbreak-notice/2011-germany-europe-e-coli.htm |archivedate=2011-06-27 }}</ref>。5月21日出現了第一例死亡病例，隔日（5月22日）德國衛生當局表示：「很清楚的，我們正面對一個異常情況。」大腸桿菌感染是有規律性的發生，在德國每年約有800～1200人遭到感染，但通常症狀是輕微的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thelocal.de/society/20110523-35185.html |title=Scientists hunt source of life-threatening stomach bug |publisher=Thelocal.de |date=2011-05-18 |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525003602/http://www.thelocal.de/society/20110523-35185.html |archive-date=2011-05-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://barfblog.foodsafety.ksu.edu/blog/148448/11/05/24/first-death-german-e-coli-outbreak-200-sick |title=First death in German ''E. coli'' outbreak; up to 200 sick | barfblog |publisher=Barfblog.foodsafety.ksu.edu |date=2011-05-24 |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719231423/http://barfblog.foodsafety.ksu.edu/blog/148448/11/05/24/first-death-german-e-coli-outbreak-200-sick |archivedate=2011-07-19 }}</ref>。至5月25日，疫情已經擴散至德國西北部的大部分地區<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.swisstribune.com/inhalt/1164-potentially-deadly-e-coli-bug-spreads-germany |title=Potentially deadly E. coli bug spreads in Germany |publisher=Swiss Tribune |date=2011-05-24 |accessdate=2011-06-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716172329/http://www.swisstribune.com/inhalt/1164-potentially-deadly-e-coli-bug-spreads-germany |archivedate=2011-07-16 }}</ref>。

2011年5月26日，德國衛生官員宣稱來自[[西班牙|西班牙]]的[[黃瓜|小黃瓜]]是導致這次德國疫情爆發的來源<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thelocal.de/national/20110526-35261.html |title=Deadly E. coli found in Spanish cucumbers - The Local |publisher=Thelocal.de |date= |accessdate=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110529092239/http://www.thelocal.de/national/20110526-35261.html |archive-date=2011-05-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。5月27日，德國官員向周圍國家發出警告，應盡速將西班牙進口的有機小黃瓜從市面上下架回收<ref name=NOTIF_REFERENCE_20110703/>。同日，[[欧洲联盟委员会|歐盟委員會]]表示西班牙[[安達盧西亞|安達卢西亞]]的兩處疑似出產帶菌小黃瓜的[[溫室|溫室]]已經關閉，並正在著手調查中<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/rasff-window/portal/index.cfm?event=notificationDetail&NOTIF_REFERENCE=2011.0703 |title=Rapid Alert System for Food and Feed |access-date=2011-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121210456/https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/rasff-window/portal/index.cfm?event=notificationDetail&NOTIF_REFERENCE=2011.0703 |archive-date=2012-01-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="bbc2">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13592765 |title=''E. coli'' cucumber scare: Germany seeks source of outbreak |publisher=BBC News Online |date=2011-05-30 |accessdate=2011-05-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5z4s65O8X?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13592765 |archivedate=2011-05-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。調查也包括分析這兩處溫室的土壤與水質樣本，檢測結果預計於6月1日出爐<ref name="tele">{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/germany/8546207/Killer-cucumbers-row-breaks-out-between-Spain-and-Germany.html |title='Killer cucumbers' row breaks out between Spain and Germany |publisher=The Telegraph |date=2011-05-30 |accessdate=2011-05-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5z4sR1sDs?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/germany/8546207/Killer-cucumbers-row-breaks-out-between-Spain-and-Germany.html |archivedate=2011-05-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。6月1日檢驗結果顯示，原認為有問題的兩處溫室所生產的小黃瓜樣本皆未遭到大腸桿菌汙染<ref>{{cite web |url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/11/366 |title=Efforts intensify to identify source of ''''E. coli''' outbreak in Germany as final tests clear Spanish cucumbers |publisher=Europa.eu |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606053619/http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO%2F11%2F366 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0601/breaking34.html |title=Europe lifts cucumber warning |publisher=The Irish Times |date=2011-06-01 |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121208234418/www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0601/breaking34.html |archive-date=2012-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msps.es/gabinetePrensa/notaPrensa/desarrolloNotaPrensa.jsp?id=2120 |title=Ministry of Health Spain |publisher=Msps.es |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720114422/http://www.msps.es/gabinetePrensa/notaPrensa/desarrolloNotaPrensa.jsp?id=2120 |archivedate=2011-07-20 }}</ref>，但這段期間藉由德國運輸與[[汉堡|汉堡]]通路網所形成的交叉汙染尚未減緩；事實上，絕大多數的可能病例是因為在德國境內所形成交叉汙染<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1392665/E-coli-outbreak-kills-Swedish-woman-death-toll-hits-16-cucumbers-NOT-blame.html|title=E.coli outbreak kills Swedish woman as death toll hits 16 but cucumbers are NOT to blame|publisher=Dailymail.co.uk|date=|accessdate=2011-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604114558/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1392665/E-coli-outbreak-kills-Swedish-woman-death-toll-hits-16-cucumbers-NOT-blame.html|archive-date=2011-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="independent1">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/health-and-families/health-news/cucumbers-in-clear-ndash-so-what-is-causing-deadly-ecoli-outbreak-2291600.html |title=Cucumbers in clear – so what is causing deadly E.coli outbreak? |publisher=The Independent |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603052934/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/health-and-families/health-news/cucumbers-in-clear-ndash-so-what-is-causing-deadly-ecoli-outbreak-2291600.html |archive-date=2011-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德國疾病管制和預防機構{{Internal link helper/en|羅伯特·科赫研究所|Robert Koch Institute}}建議停止在德國食用生[[番茄|番茄]]、[[黃瓜|小黃瓜]]及[[生菜|生菜]]，以避免疫情擴大<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rki.de/EN/Home/homepage__node.html?__nnn=true |title=Robert Koch Institute |publisher=Rki.de |date= |accessdate=2011-06-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603143700/http://www.rki.de/EN/Home/homepage__node.html?__nnn=true |archivedate=2011-06-03 }}</ref>。

