6月29日，{{Internal link helper/en|歐洲食品安全局|EFSA}}與[[歐洲疾病預防控制中心|ECDC]]公布兩方共同進行的[[风险评估|风险评估]]，文中將德國疫情與法國[[波尔多|波爾多]]地區於6月24日首次報告的溶血性尿毒綜合症疫情做了連結，該地區的幾名患者已確認感染O104:H4型大腸桿菌<ref>{{cite web |title=Cluster of haemolytic uremic syndrome (HUS) in Bordeaux, France |format=PDF |type=EFSA/ECDC joint risk-assessment |publisher=[[European_Centre_for_Disease_Prevention_and_Control|European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control]] |date=2011-06-29 |accessdate=2011-06-30 |url=http://ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications/Publications/2011June29_RA_JOINT_EFSA_STEC_France.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528171117/http://www.ecdc.europa.eu/en/publications/Publications/2011June29_RA_JOINT_EFSA_STEC_France.pdf |archive-date=2012-05-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。該評估提到2009年與2010年從[[埃及|埃及]]進口的[[葫芦巴|葫芦巴]]種籽與這次疫情或許有關聯，這批種籽已發芽過，很可能是造成兩地疫情的共同來源。為求慎重仍表示：「是否真的是汙染的共同原因，目前還有很多不確定性。」作為檢測樣本的這批種籽，目前還未發現任何O104:H4型大腸桿菌的菌株<ref>{{cite news |author=William Neuman and Scott Sayare |title=Egyptian Seeds Are Linked to E. Coli in Germany and France |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/30/world/middleeast/30ecoli.html |newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]] |date=2011-06-29 |accessdate=2011-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701020631/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/30/world/middleeast/30ecoli.html |archive-date=2011-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=James Gallagher |title=E. coli outbreaks linked to Egypt |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-13973002 |publisher=BBC News |date=2011-06-30 |accessdate=2011-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701015034/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-13973002 |archive-date=2011-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃及堅決否定葫蘆巴種籽是造成致命大腸桿菌菌株的來源，埃及農業部長認為該臆測根本是「一派胡言」<ref>{{cite news |title=Egypt denies fenugreek-German E coli link |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/health/news/article_1648784.php/Egypt-denies-fenugreek-German-E-coli-link |accessdate=2011-07-02 |newspaper=[[Monsters_and_Critics|Monsters and Critics]] |date=2011-07-01 |agency=[[Deutsche_Presse-Agentur|Deutsche Presse-Agentur]] |location=[[Cairo|Cairo]]/[[柏林|Berlin]] |quote=Egypt on Friday dismissed as untrue European reports that fenugreek seeds from Egypt were a suspected source of a deadly E coli outbreak. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818083043/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/health/news/article_1648784.php/Egypt-denies-fenugreek-German-E-coli-link |archivedate=2011-08-18 }}</ref>。

== 致病菌株 ==
{{main|大腸桿菌O104:H4型}}
[[File:E.-coli-growth.gif|thumb]]
導致這次疫情的致病菌株為[[大腸桿菌O104:H4型|大腸桿菌O104:H4型]]，這種大腸桿菌雖屬[[腸道出血性大腸桿菌|腸出血性]]，但仍攜帶部分{{Link-en|腸聚集性|enteroaggregative}}大腸桿菌的基因，並攜帶許多抗藥基因，對至少八種主要抗生素有抗藥性。腸出血性大腸桿菌的主要毒素：[[志賀氏菌屬|志賀樣毒素]]可損傷腸道黏膜，甚至進入血液中破壞[[红血球|紅血球]]，導致溶血性病變，這種症狀在[[腎|腎]]中最為明顯，常導致急性[[腎功能衰竭|腎功能衰竭]]，併發[[溶血性尿毒综合征|溶血性尿毒综合征]]<ref name="people">{{cite web|url=http://health.people.com.cn/BIG5/14936887.html|title=醫生談預防致病大腸杆菌：注意飲食避免病從口入|publisher=北京日報|date=2011-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130101123745/http://health.people.com.cn/BIG5/14936887.html|archivedate=2013-01-01|accessdate=2011-07-02}}</ref>。大部分出血性腸炎均是由O104:H7型大腸桿菌引起，這次疫情則是肇因於較罕見的O104:H4型<ref>{{vcite journal |author=Bae WK, Lee YK, Cho MS, Ma SK, Kim SW, Kim NH, ''et al.'' |title=A case of haemolytic uremic syndrome caused by ''Escherichia coli'' O104:H4 |journal=Yonsei Medical Journal |date=2006 Jun 30 |volume=47 |issue=3 |pages=473–9 |doi=10.3349/ymj.2006.47.3.437 |pmid=16807997 }}</ref><ref name="people"/>。

6月5日，中國[[深圳|深圳]]的[[华大基因|華大基因研究院]]首先完成大腸桿菌O104:H4型的基因定序<ref name="big5">{{cite web|url=http://weekly.news365.com.cn/sd/201106/t20110620_3067074.htm|title=中國速度破解“超級細菌”|publisher=新民周刊|date=2011-06-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018104640/http://weekly.news365.com.cn/sd/201106/t20110620_3067074.htm|archivedate=2011-10-18|accessdate=2016-05-18}}</ref>，經過資料比對，研究人員判斷2001年德國從腹瀉病人分離的01-09591菌株應為這次O104:H4型大腸桿菌的直接祖先，其毒性基因與本次菌株大致吻合，但本次菌株經過十年演化後，攜帶了許多以前沒有的抗藥性基因<ref name="hua2">{{cite web|url=http://www.genomics.cn/news_show.php?type=show&id=1262|title=致命大肠杆菌起源新线索|publisher=華大基因|date=2011-06-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622001802/http://www.genomics.cn/news_show.php?type=show&id=1262|archivedate=2011-06-22|accessdate=2011-07-02}}</ref>。

